overview: Brandon has provided technical and operational consulting to numerous companies and has been an important player in the multi-million dollar harvests of several companies for more than a decade. Acting as Director of Technology and Operations Management at Deer Canyon, Brandon managed $200M+ projects and created project management systems for $350M+ in assets. Brandon has now brought his experience, skills, and drive to EnticeLabs, where he oversees key aspects of our growth and ensures that the infrastructure and all core systems can support our growth.
